Inflation Instruction: Step 1: Take out the inserted white plug (air stopper) from the ball Step 2: Insert the tip of the pump into the mouth (built-in variable aperture) Step 3: Pumping the ball to proper size (usually 10 minutes for a 75cm ball) Step 4: Quickly replace the white plug back into the hole to stop air leak. Thus, keep pumping to stretch the rubber is the key.
